casebody.data:
Nelson, Respondent, v. Alexander, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. October 26, 1892.) Appeal from third district court. Action by John F. Nelson against John V. Alexander.

Argued before Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

D. A. Stephens, for appellant. G. F. Eschbach, for respondent

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
